Foreigners Sell Japan Stocks in August, 1st Monthly Sale in Year

-- B y   Y o s h i a k i   N o h a r a   a n d   S a t o s h i   K a w a n o
-- 
2011-09-08T06:04:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/foreigners-sell-japan-stocks-in-august-1st-monthly-sale-in-year.html
Overseas investors sold about 1.07
trillion yen ($13.8 billion) in Japanese shares in August, the
fourth-largest sell-off on record and the first monthly net sale
in a year, according to data from the  Tokyo  Stock Exchange.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Yoshiaki Nohara in Tokyo at 
